Package: FMIndex
Type: Package
Title: FM Index for DNA Sequences
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Negin", 
           family = "Kafee", 
           email = "negin.kafee@yahoo.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to compute the FM Index for a DNA sequence. 
    It includes the Burrows-Wheeler Transform, suffix array, occurrence table, and C table for a given DNA sequence.
